BEGIN DECLARE @salt VARCHAR(100) DECLARE @id INT
SELECT @id = Id FROM AppUser WHERE Email = @email
SELECT @salt = SaltValue FROM AppSalt WHERE UserId = @id
DECLARE @secret VARCHAR(100) SET @secret = dbo.GetSecretKey()
DECLARE @hash VARBINARY(64) SET @hash = HASHBYTES('SHA2_512', CONCAT(@Salt, @passwd, @Salt, @secret));
DECLARE @validId INT
SELECT @validId = Id FROM AppUser WHERE Email = @email AND Passwd = @hash
IF(@validId = null) BEGIN RAISERROR (15600,-1,-1, 'sp_login'); END ELSE BEGIN SELECT * FROM V_AppUser WHERE Id = @validId END END
